&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with identity, security, and data platforms is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience defining and reporting impact metrics (e.g., cost savings, cycle time reduction, productivity improvements)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
