&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Train and scale by building training resources and best-practice assets so the field team can confidently demo the latest product capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Maintain the demo environment by organizing and standardizing assets to ensure consistency, reliability, and excellence across all demos&lt;/li&gt;
